page_level.label: Install Form

elements.name: scan_label
elements.label: Scan Label
elements.dynamic_value: if(nd_device_type=="Gateway"){"Scan CUID Barcode"} else {"Scan LT barcode"}

elements.name: scanned_label
elements.label: Scanned Label
elements.dynamic_value: if(nd_device_type=="Gateway"){"CUID Number Barcode scanned"} else {"LT Number Barcode scanned"}

elements.name: invalid_barcode
elements.label: *** Please scan LT Number Barcode again **

elements.name: warning___please_check_location_accuracy__move_where_you_can_see
elements.label: Warning: [Please check location accuracy. Move where you can see clear sky to improve accuracy]

elements.name: move_label
elements.label: Distance between Surveyed and Installed is > 50ft, Please Call For Approval

elements.name: move_label_matric
elements.label: Distance between Surveyed and Installed is > 15m, Please Call For Approval

elements.name: my_element_30
elements.label: *** Install Distance cannot be greater than 250ft without approval **
elements.condition_value: Number(survey_to_install_distance)>250 && check_lt_number=="Correct LT Number" && move_approved_by=="" && is_move_needed.sort_order==0 && unit_of_measure=="us"

elements.name: my_element_84
elements.label: *** Install Distance cannot be greater than 76m without approval **
elements.condition_value: Number(survey_to_install_distance)>76 && check_lt_number=="Correct LT Number" && move_approved_by=="" && is_move_needed.sort_order==0 && unit_of_measure=="metric"

elements.name: install_distance_notes
elements.label: Install Distance Notes
elements.condition_value: (Number(survey_to_install_distance)>150 && check_lt_number=="Correct LT Number" && unit_of_measure=="us") || (Number(survey_to_install_distance)>45 && check_lt_number=="Correct LT Number" && unit_of_measure=="metric")
